    &lt;version&gt;CURRENT-VERSION&lt;/version&gt;
&lt;/dependency&gt;
```

is used (e.g. listed in pom.xml).

The JPA Metamodel can be used with the JPA Criteria API, see also [here](https://www.baeldung.com/hibernate-criteria-queries-metamodel).

